Class CapabilityDeploymentProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.itinfrastructure.properties.ConfigurationItemRelationshipProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.itinfrastructure.properties.CapabilityDeploymentProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CapabilityDeploymentProperties extends ConfigurationItemRelationshipProperties
CapabilityDeploymentProperties describes the properties for the SupportedSoftwareCapability relationship between a ITInfrastructure asset and a Software Capability.
